<details class="wp-block-details" style="padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--xxs);padding-right:0;padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--xxs);padding-left:0"><summary>How do I create a child theme?</summary><!-- wp:paragraph {"placeholder":"Type / to add a hidden block"} -->
